      <bioghist id="aspace_b9972ca1d72c4deef84f9b21e96f0587">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Scott Helmes is an artist and visual poet, active in St. Paul, Minnesota.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_359aeefa961821856a28ef170fb211e9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains a selection of artworks by visual poet Scott Helmes, including examples of editioned prints from his <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Haiku</part>
            </title> series.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_6529c4fbf3188f2767e7288f7bce6ae4">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into two series: I. Works, 2009-2010. II. Correspondence, 2010.</p>  
      </arrangement>
